         <repository label="Repository:">Division of Rare and Manuscript Collections, Cornell University Library.</repository>
         <abstract label="Abstract:">Newspapers and magazines reporting major events during World War I and II.</abstract>
         <langmaterial label="Language:">Collection material in <language encodinganalog="041" langcode="eng">English</language>
         </langmaterial>
      </did>
      <scopecontent encodinganalog="MARC 520">
         <head id="a3">COLLECTION DESCRIPTION</head>
         <p>Newspapers and magazines reporting the Armistice being signed (Nov. 1918) and major events during World War II (1941-49), including the 
		<title>Washington Times Herald</title>; <title>Washington Post</title>; <title>New York Times</title>; <title>Baltimore News-Post</title>; <title>Washington Daily News</title>; <title>Philadelphia Inquirer</title>; <title>Daily Mirror</title>; <title>Baltimore American</title>; <title>Evening Star</title>; <title>Minneapolis Journal</title>; <title>Wisconsin State Journal</title>; <title>Madison Democrat</title>; <title>Yank: the Army Weekly</title> and <title>The Voice of Victory</title>.</p>
      </scopecontent>
